{"tid":2398348,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"閱讀次子Hunter自傳 拜登：這本書帶給我希望","createTime":"2021-02-07T08:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T10:43:19.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"de96080a70b0ea0d2e4c2449a345df4c61ef5912","tid":2398348,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T08:23:02.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕深陷醜聞纏身的美國總統拜登次子杭特（Hunter Biden）將出版自傳，自述年少時如何因各種問題而沉迷酒精和藥物，拜登表示已經閱讀過兒子的自傳，他表示感覺到兒子挺身而出面對這些問題，讚「我的男孩回來了」，認為讀著讀著就帶給他希望。<br />\n<br />\n由出版商藝廊書店（Gallery Books）出版、名為《美麗事物》（Beautiful Things，暫譯）的拜登次子杭特自傳預計4月問世，美國總統拜登接受《哥倫比亞廣播公司》（CBS）專訪時指出 ，他閱讀過兒子的自傳了，杭特站出來坦然面對的態度，讓他感覺「我的男孩回來了」。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3435101\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3435101&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOe9tl09raJ%2B2zMWOssuGUT0%3D&h=5cd32ee6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3435101&h=1be4933a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3435101</a>"},{"pid":"b0047f9ed7a01bbe593b955b23d90d6891a5b074","tid":2398348,"uid":110832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T08:23:49.000Z","msg":"廢登好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad65a4ded1fdd0ea3dd4ad485ae0e2ad3eeda5d3","tid":2398348,"uid":36383,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T08:25:22.000Z","msg":"拜登讀完之後嗰一日: What did he write <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"f089fdf1a525020e1b72d31feead9e